thread.title: Jonna Jugas

author: Jonna Jugas
title: Jonna Jugas
text:
Good focus and work with more sustainable clothing, good price and feels like an honest clothingchain! Good quality, enviormental focus (BIG UPS) and good look, more of that in your everyday shops please! Love a genuine female store, with a good blend of taste and different women. A place we all can meet, new-moms, career-moms, students and business-women and shop eco-friendly! Night out, meetings and cozy sleepovers and a good bra for every occasion!
/jjk
